  <brief_title>The Effectiveness of Pasteurized Goat Milk in the Treatment of Childhood Oral Ulcer Diseases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1 1 Study Assesing the Benefit of Pasteurized Goat Milk in Reducing Disease Severity of Young Children With Oral Ulcer Diseases</official_title>
  <sponsors>
